  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n<img width=\"274\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-05-19 at 11 34 47\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/82375995/9f4252a5-b99c-4487-8820-f18c5e3269dd\">\r\n\r\n1. create community\r\n2. in several chats send `@everyone` mentioning\r\n3. create new user and add it to the community\r\n4. allow this user to fetch messages\r\n\r\nAs the result, user is receiving mentions from the past messages when he was not a part of community yet",
